{"type":null,"faqId":32679,"title":"WLAN不定时断开重连，提示“已连接XXX网络”怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.19861111in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.0826389in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1、  </span><span>连接 WLAN 成功后，请保持在 WLAN 热点的有效距离内，避免由于距离太远导致网络信号弱从而自动断开。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2、  </span><span>进入 WLAN 设置界面，点击“高级设置 &gt; 在休眠状态下保持 WLAN 连接”，选择“始终”。手机将始终保持与 WLAN 网络的连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3、  </span><span>若问题依然存在，请重新打开 WLAN 开关或重启 WLAN 热点。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7381","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748380000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":14,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"WLAN,断开重连","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}